OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFresh west to northwest winds
OL,6,Fbringing cloudy skies and occasional
OL,7,Fshowers this morning. Gradually
OL,8,Fturning drier and brighter through the
OL,9,Fafternoon as the winds ease.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMost staying dry with the
OL,12,Fsouth seeing the best of the late
OL,13,Fsunshine. However a few light showers
OL,14,Fcropping up around the coasts.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FSome patchy light rain
OL,17,Fpossible in the south and west, but
OL,18,Fmost staying dry and seeing spells of
OL,19,Fhazy sunshine. Winds light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
