OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,6,Fstart to Monday with hazy sunshine.
OL,7,FHowever, occasional areas of rain
OL,8,Fcrossing the Province from the
OL,9,Fsouthwest from later Monday and
OL,10,Fthrough Tuesday and Wednesday.
